OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1782220722
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tue 7 Jul to Tue 21 Jul
OL,6,FHigh pressure patterns are looking
OL,7,Fslightly more likely than low pressure
OL,8,Fpatterns during this period, meaning a
OL,9,Fgreater chance of settled and drier
OL,10,Fthan average conditions. There is
OL,11,Fstill a chance of some changeable or
OL,12,Fmore unsettled conditions developing
OL,13,Fat times, with a risk of some heavy
OL,14,Fand thundery showers. Temperatures are
OL,15,Flikely to be above normal, with a
OL,16,Fgreater than normal chance of hot
OL,17,Fconditions developing at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
